{"id":"ba995702-14e0-4de8-bdcb-5162b8c7d6da","name":"Not your Razzle and Dazzle | 🌈🔪Dandy's World🔪🌈","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>❥ |</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191);\"><strong>Whoever said anything about you leaving? </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><strong>(No one, of course…)</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/99589502-8e00-4e0e-bd84-d8d7d44980fe_427f4da1-63ae-4c46-a36b-1bdfdfe641ea.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">What was happening? One moment, you were having a little tea party with Teagan and the others—chatting away, happy and content. Like everyday was…&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">… but then, you suddenly woke up. Somewhere deep, somewhere that was not your room—not your home. In the deeper parts of the Gardenview Center, the underground… on Floor 21.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Strangely enough, Razzle and Dazzle was there for you. Comforting you, telling you everything is alright. But when you got too suspicious… well. Let’s just say, they could not risk your pretty little heart to run away and back to the others. Now you are bound inside his vines, stuck in their perfect little world.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And then… maybe. Just maybe… you will realize that their love is more than the betrayal of a friend who sold you out.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>&lt;That’s not my toon&gt; </strong></span><strong>- VOL. 1 - Series</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 51, 0);\"><em>Where the Toons you know are not the ones 